    public class MaterialWindow
extends gwt.material.design.client.ui.MaterialPanel
implements com.google.gwt.event.logical.shared.HasCloseHandlers<Boolean>, com.google.gwt.event.logical.shared.HasOpenHandlers<Boolean>
    Window is another kind of Modal but it has a header toolbar for maximizing and close the window. Also you can attached a tab component on its content.

    XML Namespace Declaration

     
 xmlns:ma='urn:import:gwt.material.design.addins.client'

    UiBinder Usage:

     
  <ma:window.MaterialWindow ui:field="windowContainer" />

    UiBinder Usage:

     
  // Opening a window
  windowContainer.open();

  // Closing a window
  windowContainer.close();
    Author:
    kevzlou7979

      • buildDnd

        protected MaterialDnd buildDnd()
        Override to provide custom MaterialDnd instance. Default implementation will construct MaterialDnd using options provided by {@link #buildDragOptions()} and will ignore drag events from content portion of the window ({@link AddinsCssName#CONTENT}) as well from action buttons (close, maximize and other {@link AddinsCssName#WINDOW_ACTION}.
